Hey!
I need to add a query parameter to the redirectURL on a form submission. I've been thinking, instead of redirecting a form to a page in the thank you settings, i set a inline thank you message and redirect programatically with my query parameter. However then i will loose the submissionGuid as a query parameter.

Anybody know how i can attach the submissionGuid manually? (Where to get it from)

My solution so far:
```window.addEventListener("message", (event) =&gt; {
  if (
    event.data.type === "hsFormCallback" &amp;&amp;
    event.data.eventName === "onFormSubmitted"
  ) {
    //REDIRECT TO PAGE WITH CUSTOM QUERY PARAMETERS AND APPEND THE submissionGuid
  }
});```
